id: pm-btwe
title: Add importer/exporter options arg and command-def examples to SDK.md
description: "PR #94 (2026-06-01) added an optional 3rd options argument to registerImporter/registerExporter enabling full command definition with flags. SDK.md has a basic registerImporter/registerExporter section (around line 478-520) but does not show the options arg for command definition, which is the primary use case for first-party packages like pm-beads and pm-todos."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[4]: "area:docs",extensions,importers,sdk
created_at: "2026-06-07T10:08:04.897Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-09T18:41:22.084Z"
author: audit-docs-tests-agent
acceptance_criteria: "- SDK.md registerImporter/registerExporter section shows the optional 3rd arg with a command-definition example\n- The example includes at minimum: command name, flags, description\n- The pm-beads or pm-todos pattern is cited as a first-party reference implementation"
parent: pm-u9d0
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: Verified SDK docs include importer/exporter options arg and command definition examples as part of the SDK docs bundle.
expected_result: SDK docs give package authors practical command and importer/exporter examples.
actual_result: SDK docs remain linked and validated; this branch also links to the new command-kit exemplar.
