body: "## Context\nFrom memory session 2026-06-01: 'SDK first-class importer/exporter registration (pm-7qjk: registerImporter/registerExporter optional 3rd options arg → full command def+flags)'\n\ndocs/SDK.md line 478: 'registerImporter(name, importer) and registerExporter(name, exporter) register...'\ndocs/SDK.md line 493: shows registerImporter with only 2 args\ndocs/SDK.md line 516: shows registerExporter 'jsonl' with only 2 args\n\nThe 3rd options argument (command definition with flags) is not shown in any SDK.md example.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- SDK.md registerImporter/registerExporter section shows the optional 3rd arg with a command-definition example\n- The example includes at minimum: command name, flags, description\n- The pm-beads or pm-todos pattern is cited as a first-party reference implementation\n\n## Evidence\ndocs/SDK.md lines 478-520; docs/examples/starter-extension/index.js lines 160-165 (only 2-arg form); memory note 2026-06-01 pm-7qjk"
